sequenceDiagram
    participant DAG as DAG Engine
    participant RAG as RAGConfigBenchmarkNode
    participant Scorer as FaithfulnessRelevanceScorerNode

    DAG->>RAG: execute(inputs)
    activate RAG
    Note over RAG: Runs vector retrieval & LLM generation
    RAG-->>DAG: { ..., "context": "chunk1, chunk2", "response": "LLM output text" }
    deactivate RAG

    DAG->>Scorer: execute({ "context_source": "node_RAG", "response_source": "node_RAG" })
    activate Scorer
    Note over Scorer: Resolves upstream refs
    Scorer->>DAG: Fetch state["node_RAG"]["context"]
    Scorer->>DAG: Fetch state["node_RAG"]["response"]
    Note over Scorer: Computes LLM-as-a-judge metrics
    Scorer-->>DAG: { "faithfulness_score": 0.85, "relevance_score": 0.92 }
    deactivate Scorer